      <abstract id="aspace_d05b9e5a40b676aed9e62bf0b454fcfd">The An American Family Collection consists of 12 one-hour episodes of the 12-hour documentary, "An American Family," that debuted on PBS-TV in early 1973. It consists of 12 DVDs.</abstract>
      <langmaterial><language langcode="eng">English</language>
.    </langmaterial>
