    <arrangement id="aspace_87536e9db64dc8dd0a5ca81ee0d85e3d">
      <head>Arrangement</head>
      <p>The episodes are arranged in the order in which they originally aired on PBS-TV, 1973.</p>
    </arrangement>
    <scopecontent id="aspace_55a70903d0713b63a57295dfa5085422">
      <head>Scope and Content note</head>
      <p>The collection is comprised of 12 one-hour episodes that document the Loud's day-to-day life during seven months of 1971.</p>
    </scopecontent>
